197
00:11:03,950 --> 00:11:07,320
Jika terjadi sesuatu, pasti di antara waktu-waktu itu.

198
00:11:08,119 --> 00:11:09,459
An Soon Jin.

199
00:11:11,829 --> 00:11:14,160
