212
00:12:08,780 --> 00:12:12,589
"Nenek, tolong belikan aku 'Jeli Menggeliat dan Aku'."

213
00:12:13,959 --> 00:12:16,690
Anak kecil itu mengikutiku ke mana-mana.

214
00:12:18,890 --> 00:12:20,060
Aku

215
