217
00:12:34,009 --> 00:12:35,109
Kyung Soo.

218
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:38,249
Teganya pria seperti itu...

219
00:12:38,249 --> 00:12:40,780
Kenapa? Kenapa harus dia?

220
